---
title: Creamy Truffle and Mushroom Rigatoni with Walnuts and Tenderstem Broccoli
description: A decadent dinner that takes only 20 minutes to whip up?  Yes please! An indulgent creamy and garlicky sauce balanced with bitter greens for the perfect pasta dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-truffle-and-mushroom-pasta-c4951678-e4be4852.jpg
